text: Not much of attraction bcoz this restricted area only authorised working people with special passcard allow to enter the main gate. Canteen only have 1 Indian stall and drink stall plus severalvending machine for working people. AC environment.
More of a place to eat your own food, only one indian stall vendor, no drink stalls only vending machine, but clean and ac canteen
Good canteen, love it here! my go to place and people are just nice here
